description.full: This game was classified by the community with the following category scores - Violence=1/3, Sex=0/3, Mature Content=0/3. Take to the skies in frenetic WWII dogfighting. Fight it out with up to 10 aircraft - friend and foe! Multiple flyable aircraft. Single player & 2 player battles - including cooperative play. [website http://sharky.bluecog.co.nz]
